details.title: AESS published tutorial
details.abstract: Copies of tutorials are available for use by any AESS function, as long as stocks last. Requests must indicate the Tutorial Number and quantity (minimum of 25), by in writing, provide a complete street shipping address including telephone number, give adequate lead time for fulfillment, and indicate the date desired at the destination. Direct your requests to Judy Scharmann by e-mail at j.scharmann@ieee.org or contact her by phone at 785-317-8741.
details.journal_title: IEEE Aerospace and Electronic Systems Magazine
